metadata.description:
Chapter 1: Repercussions

An evil being, people called it “Ethrum”, he emerges from the north.

Many people believe that he is a creature sent by God to destroy mankind because greed has grown out of control and exceeds our wisdom.

—

Dead Ghost, 2022.
4960x7016 px | @300 dpi.
